data.title: Willie Nelson Abbott Texas OS Tee – GREY LAYNE
data.meta_description: Pay homage to the origin of Willie Nelson’s roots with a proven fan-favorite graphic, reimagined on a brown, distressed wash OS tee. Featuring a country inspired eagle with the outlaw’s name in western letters and a special shoutout to Nelson’s hometown of Abbott, Texas.
